controllers

Class GameController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controllers.GameController

  • public class GameController
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the controller to control the running of the game. The game is multiple users game, a local file "game.json" is used to communicate. So there is a class MyTask to handle the state sync. MyTask will runs every 500ms.
